# Title: RottenPotato Like Attack Pattern
# Author: @SBousseaden, Florian Roth
# Date: 2019-11-15
# Level: high
# Description: Detects logon events that have characteristics of events generated during an attack with RottenPotato and the like
# MITRE Tactic: Collection
# Tags: attack.collection, attack.privilege-escalation, attack.credential-access, attack.t1557.001
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/builtin/security/account_management/win_security_susp_rottenpotato.yml

EventID=4624 IpAddress IN ("127.0.0.1", "::1") LogonType=3 TargetUserName="ANONYMOUS LOGON" WorkstationName="-"